<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de-CH">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#2F6B5F">
  <title>FamilyOS – Offline</title>
  <style>
    body { margin:0; min-height:100vh; display:grid; place-items:center;
      font-family:system-ui,sans-serif; background:#f7f8f7; color:#173c34; }
    main { max-width:520px; padding:32px; text-align:center; }
    img { width:96px; border-radius:26px; }
    button { border:0; border-radius:999px; padding:12px 20px;
      background:#2f6b5f; color:white; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <img src="icons/Icon-192.png" alt="">
    <h1>Du bist offline</h1>
    <p>Bereits geladene Bereiche von FamilyOS bleiben verfügbar. Stelle die Internetverbindung wieder her und versuche es erneut.</p>
    <button onclick="location.reload()">Erneut versuchen</button>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
